Class JsHoister.Cloner

java.lang.Object

      com.google.gwt.dev.js.JsHoister.Cloner
Enclosing class:
JsHoister
public static class JsHoister.Cloner
extends JsVisitor

Implements actual cloning logic. We rely on the JsExpressions to provide traversal logic. The stack field is used to accumulate already-cloned JsExpression instances. One gotcha that falls out of this is that argument lists are on the stack in reverse order, so lists should be constructed via inserts, rather than appends.
